::Epyon/Skyburst::

They arrived at the cell.
"Get in there Nightstrike," said Epyon.

OOC: Okay Airly, now is your chance.

BIC: ::Prowl/Hot Rod::

Prowl saw Azure following.
"Okay, I have no problem with you coming, Azure."
He then looked ahead and saw that Hot Rod was much farther ahead. He
would reach the stranded bots first. Then their comm message came in.
He replyed, "Understood. Three of us are coming. You'll probably see a
red Cybertronian sport car first. That will be Hot Rod, one of my
troops."
